{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1740949788.534067", "card_id": "Q_13817925698", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "蔡明称因常年不吃早饭导致胆摘除，这和不吃早饭关系大吗？不吃早饭有哪些坏处？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，综艺节目《一路繁花》中，演员蔡明表示自己不能多吃韭菜，张蔷说胆不好的人不能多吃，而蔡明听完后解释称，自己没有胆，因为常年不吃早饭所以摘除了。 蔡明表示，「胆结石在胆里待着就没事，一旦你一晃，那石头就卡在胆管里了」，还说胆结石疼起来疼得想撞墙。 「切了胆之后，那个胆里又是石头又是沙子。」蔡明说。 2021 年 3 月，蔡明被曝出有胆结石，网上一组照片显示，蔡明在录制节目时突发不适，被送往医院。事后蔡明发微博回应自己「被紧急送医」：胆结石突发，目前病情已经稳定。 63 岁演员蔡明自曝「胆被摘除了」，因常年不吃早饭"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-5ce9a20260957c4625e6325c8a9d8175_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "236 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/13817925698"}}, "attached_info": "CkII5siT3Iaf1OgDEAMaCTExMzczOTAxMSDAq4++BjAAOJEDQAByCzEzODE3OTI1Njk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1740949788.535015", "card_id": "Q_13733505856", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 36}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "DeepSeek 官方测算模型成本利润率为 545%，这个数字意味着什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "DeepSeek：DeepSeek-V3 / R1 推理系统概览"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-26f069dbfd803c157a23ea7a97d717f2_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "83 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/13733505856"}}, "attached_info": "CkII5siT3Iaf1OgDEAMaCTExMzcyMjIwMSDhrIq+BjAAOJgCQAFyCzEzNzMzNTA1ODU2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1740949788.535302", "card_id": "